 <body region="横下" xml:space="preserve"> 
  <div> 
   <p begin="00:00:02.336" end="00:00:03.879" style="s1"><span style="s2">（ナレーション）<br /><span style="s3">ポケモンコントロールマシンで—</span></span></p> 
   <p begin="00:00:03.963" end="00:00:06.841" style="s4"><span style="s2">あらゆるポケモンを操ってしまう<br />プラズマ団</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:00:07.341" end="00:00:08.926" style="s4"><span style="s2">その究極の目的は—</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:00:09.009" end="00:00:12.513" style="s4"><span style="s2">伝説と呼ばれしポケモン<br />レシラムを我がものとし—</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:00:13.013" end="00:00:14.765" style="s4"><span style="s2">世界を制圧することだった</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:00:15.433" end="00:00:19.019" style="s4"><span style="s2">そして<span style="s5"><span style="s6">彼</span><span style="s7">かれ</span></span>らは ついに<br />ライトストーンを手に入れ—</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:00:19.103" end="00:00:21.856" style="s4"><span style="s2">レシラム復活の<span style="s5"><span style="s6">儀式</span><span style="s7">ぎしき</span></span>を<br />始めたのだった</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:00:22.857" end="00:00:26.110" style="s4"><span style="s2">果たして レシラムは Ｎは…</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:00:26.610" end="00:00:29.029" style="s4"><span style="s2">サトシたちの運命は？</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:00:31.532" end="00:00:33.534" region="縦右">♪～</p> 
   <p begin="00:01:56.992" end="00:01:58.994" region="縦右">～♪</p> 
   <p begin="00:02:02.373" end="00:02:06.585" style="s1"><span style="s2">（サトシ）<span style="s3">“レシラム対Ｎ！</span><br /><span style="s3">理想と真実の彼方(かなた)へ!!”</span></span></p> 
   <p begin="00:02:11.090" end="00:02:12.967" style="s1"><span style="s2">（ゲーチス）ライトストーンよ！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:02:13.050" end="00:02:15.886" style="s1"><span style="s2">伝説と呼ばれしポケモン<br />レシラムよ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:02:15.970" end="00:02:18.347" style="s1"><span style="s2">今こそ その姿を見せよ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:02:18.430" end="00:02:21.350" style="s1"><span style="s2">人の世に真実の光を照らせ！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:02:25.479" end="00:02:27.690" style="s1"><span style="s2">（サトシ）プラズマ団 やめろ！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:02:30.734" end="00:02:32.027" style="s1"><span style="s2">（アンジー）なんだ この<span style="s5"><span style="s6">霧</span><span style="s7">きり</span></span>は…</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:02:33.279" end="00:02:35.531" style="s1"><span style="s2">（アイリス）これって…<br />（デント）あの２人が？</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:02:38.284" end="00:02:39.743" style="s1"><span style="s2">（アンジーたち）うわあ！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:02:39.827" end="00:02:40.828" style="s1"><span style="s2">（Ｎ）あっ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:02:43.497" end="00:02:45.332" style="s1"><span style="s2">サイケこうせんと<br />マジカルリーフだ！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:02:45.416" end="00:02:47.293" style="s1"><span style="s2"><span style="s5"><span style="s6">間違</span><span style="s7">まちが</span></span>いないわ あの２人よ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:02:47.376" end="00:02:51.255" style="s1"><span style="s2">ヘレナさんとバーベナさんが<br />Ｎさんを助けに来たんだ！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:02:51.338" end="00:02:51.922" style="s1"><span style="s2">（ピカチュウ）ピ～カ！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:02:52.840" end="00:02:54.592" style="s1"><span style="s2">キバゴ キバゴ　ちょっと聞いて</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:02:55.092" end="00:02:56.093" style="s1"><span style="s2">（キバゴ）キバ？</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:02:56.176" end="00:02:57.970" style="s1"><span style="s2">このベルト <span style="s5"><span style="s6">壊</span><span style="s7">こわ</span></span>してくれない？</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:02:58.053" end="00:02:58.888" style="s1"><span style="s2">（キバゴ）キバ！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:03:03.017" end="00:03:05.769" style="s1"><span style="s2">その調子よ <span style="s5"><span style="s6">頑張</span><span style="s7">がんば</span></span>って キバゴ！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:03:06.896" end="00:03:10.399" style="s1"><span style="s2">（ヘレナ）<br />Ｎ あなたの心は<span style="s5"><span style="s6">汚</span><span style="s8">けが</span></span>れてしまった</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:03:11.442" end="00:03:15.112" style="s1"><span style="s2">（バーベナ）一体 あなたに<br />何が宿ったというのですか？</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:03:15.946" end="00:03:18.657" style="s1"><span style="s2">（Ｎ）<br />ヘレナ バーベナ 聞いてくれ！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:03:18.741" end="00:03:20.868" style="s1"><span style="s2">レシラムが今<br />目覚めようとしている！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:03:21.702" end="00:03:23.787" style="s4"><span style="s2">このままでは<br />２年前のあの日と同じ—</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:03:24.413" end="00:03:27.041" style="s4"><span style="s2"><span style="s5"><span style="s6">破壊</span><span style="s7">はかい</span></span>の悲劇が <span style="s5"><span style="s6">繰</span><span style="s7">く</span></span>り返されてしまう</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:03:29.293" end="00:03:31.253" style="s1"><span style="s2">ボクは レシラムが なぜ—</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:03:31.337" end="00:03:33.589" style="s1"><span style="s2">あんなにも<span style="s5"><span style="s6">怒</span><span style="s7">いか</span></span>りを<span style="s5"><span style="s6">抱</span><span style="s7">いだ</span></span>いたのか<br />知りたい</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:03:34.089" end="00:03:36.050" style="s1"><span style="s2">知らなければ 理解し合えない</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:03:36.133" end="00:03:37.134" style="s1"><span style="s2">（団員）<span style="s5"><span style="s6">黙</span><span style="s7">だま</span></span>れ！<br />（Ｎ）うっ…</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:03:37.885" end="00:03:39.219" style="s1"><span style="s2">（Ｎ）理解しなければ—</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:03:39.303" end="00:03:41.639" style="s1"><span style="s2">ポケモンと人の理想の未来など—</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:03:41.722" end="00:03:42.723" style="s1"><span style="s2">ありは しないんだ！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:03:43.307" end="00:03:44.224" style="s1"><span style="s2">ボクはレシラムに—</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:03:44.308" end="00:03:45.476" style="s1"><span style="s2">人間を信じてほしい！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:03:47.603" end="00:03:49.229" style="s1"><span style="s2">（ヘレナ）帰りましょう Ｎ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:03:49.313" end="00:03:51.523" style="s1"><span style="s2">（バーベナ）<br />あなたを失うわけにはいかない</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:03:51.607" end="00:03:53.484" style="s1"><span style="s2">ボクは<span style="s5"><span style="s6">逃</span><span style="s7">に</span></span>げない！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:03:53.567" end="00:03:55.903" style="s1"><span style="s2">ポケモンたちの<br />真の幸福を願うなら—</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:03:56.528" end="00:03:58.697" style="s1"><span style="s2">ボクたちと<span style="s5"><span style="s6">一緒</span><span style="s7">いっしょ</span></span>に戦ってくれ！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:04:00.074" end="00:04:01.825" style="s1"><span style="s2">サーナイトとゴチルゼル！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:04:01.909" end="00:04:04.536" style="s1"><span style="s2">（アンジー）<br />ドクター･アクロマ ポケモンだ！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:04:04.620" end="00:04:05.955" style="s1"><span style="s2"><span style="s5"><span style="s6">霧</span><span style="s7">きり</span></span>の中の目を<span style="s5"><span style="s6">狙</span><span style="s7">ねら</span></span>え！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:04:06.038" end="00:04:06.914" style="s1"><span style="s2">（アクロマ）<span style="s5"><span style="s6">了解</span><span style="s7">りょうかい</span></span></span></p> 
   <p begin="00:04:10.084" end="00:04:11.335" style="s1"><span style="s2">（サーナイト）サナ…<br />（ゴチルゼル）ゴチル…</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:04:15.005" end="00:04:15.798" style="s1"><span style="s2">（Ｎ）あっ！<br />（サトシ）しまった！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:04:16.382" end="00:04:17.841" style="s1"><span style="s2">（アンジー）よし お前たち！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:04:17.925" end="00:04:21.261" style="s1"><span style="s2">我々 プラズマ団のために<br />その力を<span style="s5"><span style="s6">振</span><span style="s8">ふ</span></span>るうのだ！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:04:22.513" end="00:04:23.889" style="s1"><span style="s2"><span style="s5"><span style="s6">愚</span><span style="s7">おろ</span></span>か者めが</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:04:25.766" end="00:04:27.267" style="s1"><span style="s2">（ヘレナ）<br />どうしたのです？　サーナイト</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:04:28.060" end="00:04:30.312" style="s1"><span style="s2">（バーベナ）<br />ゴチルゼル Ｎを助けるのです！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:04:30.396" end="00:04:31.647" style="s1"><span style="s2">（サーナイト）サーナ！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:04:31.730" end="00:04:33.440" style="s1"><span style="s2">（２人）きゃ～！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:04:33.524" end="00:04:34.608" style="s1"><span style="s2">うわっ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:04:35.484" end="00:04:36.485" style="s1"><span style="s2">（２人）うう…</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:04:36.568" end="00:04:40.239" style="s1"><span style="s2">（アンジー）お前たちのポケモンは<br />もはや 我々の兵器と化した</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:04:44.326" end="00:04:45.619" style="s1"><span style="s2">応えよ レシラム</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:04:46.495" end="00:04:50.290" style="s1"><span style="s2">お前の<span style="s5"><span style="s6">再臨</span><span style="s7">さいりん</span></span>を<br />我々は待ち望んでいるのだ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:04:55.754" end="00:04:56.672" style="s1"><span style="s2">フッ…</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:04:57.256" end="00:04:58.048" style="s1"><span style="s2">あ…</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:05:07.433" end="00:05:10.477" style="s1"><span style="s2">（レシラム）レシラーム！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:05:10.561" end="00:05:12.271" style="s1"><span style="s2">おお！　レシラム！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:05:12.354" end="00:05:13.105" style="s1"><span style="s2">あっ…</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:05:14.023" end="00:05:16.900" style="s1"><span style="s2">（アイリス）<br />あれが伝説と呼ばれしポケモン—</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:05:17.401" end="00:05:18.569" style="s1"><span style="s2">レシラムなの？</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:05:19.653" end="00:05:20.904" style="s1"><span style="s2">キバ！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:05:20.988" end="00:05:22.364" style="s1"><span style="s2">ありがとう キバゴ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:05:22.448" end="00:05:23.866" style="s1"><span style="s2">次は デントをお願い！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:05:23.949" end="00:05:24.783" style="s1"><span style="s2">キバ！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:05:28.620" end="00:05:29.204" style="s1"><span style="s2">レシラム！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:05:36.879" end="00:05:37.921" style="s1"><span style="s2">ああ…</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:05:39.381" end="00:05:42.051" style="s1"><span style="s2">レシラムよ 私はゲーチス</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:05:43.093" end="00:05:46.096" style="s1"><span style="s2">お前を待ち望んでいたのは<br />この私だ！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:05:47.431" end="00:05:48.640" style="s1"><span style="s2">ラーッ！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:05:48.724" end="00:05:50.517" style="s1"><span style="s2">やはり <span style="s5"><span style="s6">怒</span><span style="s7">いか</span></span>りを<span style="s5"><span style="s6">抱</span><span style="s7">いだ</span></span>くか</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:05:51.018" end="00:05:53.270" style="s1"><span style="s2">だが お前は我々の兵器となる！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:05:53.353" end="00:05:55.314" style="s1"><span style="s2">レシラーム！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:05:55.397" end="00:05:56.815" style="s1"><span style="s2">では 始めましょう</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:05:57.524" end="00:05:58.025" style="s1"><span style="s2">発射！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:06:03.489" end="00:06:05.491" style="s1"><span style="s2">（苦しむ声）</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:06:05.574" end="00:06:06.700" style="s1"><span style="s2">（サトシ）ああっ！<br />（Ｎ）あっ！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:06:06.784" end="00:06:09.787" style="s1"><span style="s2">私の<span style="s5"><span style="s6">完璧</span><span style="s7">かんぺき</span></span>なる技術の前には—</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:06:09.870" end="00:06:11.747" style="s1"><span style="s2"><span style="s5"><span style="s6">屈服</span><span style="s7">くっぷく</span></span>するほかないのです</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:06:11.830" end="00:06:13.874" style="s1"><span style="s2">さあさあ レシラム</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:06:13.957" end="00:06:16.460" style="s1"><span style="s2">力の全てを解放してください</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:06:17.086" end="00:06:17.711" style="s1"><span style="s2">フフッ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:06:19.546" end="00:06:22.758" style="s1"><span style="s2">（アクロマ）レシラムは今<br />人間の支配下に置かれました</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:06:23.801" end="00:06:25.427" style="s1"><span style="s2">すばらしい</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:06:25.511" end="00:06:27.221" style="s1"><span style="s2">私が すばらしい！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:06:27.805" end="00:06:29.264" style="s1"><span style="s2">ああ…</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:06:29.348" end="00:06:31.141" style="s1"><span style="s2">よし レシラム</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:06:31.225" end="00:06:36.021" style="s1"><span style="s2">プラズマ団のせん兵として<br />はむかう者 全てを焼き<span style="s5"><span style="s6">払</span><span style="s8">はら</span></span>え！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:06:38.524" end="00:06:39.233" style="s1"><span style="s2">（Ｎ）何！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:06:39.316" end="00:06:40.609" style="s1"><span style="s2">うわっ！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:06:44.738" end="00:06:45.864" style="s1"><span style="s2">（サトシ）うっ…</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:06:45.948" end="00:06:46.990" style="s1"><span style="s2">（２人）うっ…</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:06:49.243" end="00:06:51.161" style="s1"><span style="s2">（ハンサム）<br /><span style="s5"><span style="s6">逃</span><span style="s8">に</span></span>げろ 巻き<span style="s5"><span style="s6">込</span><span style="s8">こ</span></span>まれるぞ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:06:52.538" end="00:06:55.666" style="s1"><span style="s2">（ニャース）<br />ニャ～ 熱いのニャ～！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:06:55.749" end="00:06:57.376" style="s1"><span style="s2">（コジロウ）<br />すごいな あのマシン！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:06:57.459" end="00:06:59.336" style="s1"><span style="s2">（ムサシ）ええ すごすぎよ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:06:59.419" end="00:07:01.171" style="s1"><span style="s2">レシラムまで操れるなんて！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:07:09.721" end="00:07:11.140" style="s1"><span style="s2">（アンジー）うわっ<br />（ブラッド）ああ～</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:07:13.684" end="00:07:15.561" style="s1"><span style="s2">（ハンサム）うわっ うっ…</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:07:15.644" end="00:07:16.603" style="s1"><span style="s2">ハッ… しめた！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:07:16.687" end="00:07:19.439" style="s1"><span style="s2">（ニャース）ニャ！<br />（ドッコラー）ドッコ！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:07:25.028" end="00:07:27.406" style="s1"><span style="s2">クロスフレイム<br />これほどのパワーとは！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:07:27.489" end="00:07:30.033" style="s1"><span style="s2">何よ！　あのゲーチスってヤツ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:07:30.117" end="00:07:32.411" style="s1"><span style="s2">部下が巻き<span style="s5"><span style="s6">添</span><span style="s7">ぞ</span></span>えになっても<br />おかまいなしかよ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:07:32.494" end="00:07:35.455" style="s1"><span style="s2">（アクロマ）<br />これはこれは すばらしい数値です</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:07:35.539" end="00:07:36.957" style="s1"><span style="s2">ですが レシラム…</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:07:39.168" end="00:07:43.046" style="s1"><span style="s2">あなたのポテンシャルは<br />まだまだ こんなものではないはず</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:07:44.423" end="00:07:46.508" style="s1"><span style="s2">ラーッ！</span></p> 
